[src:python/datetime-p01] Return the day of the week as an integer, where Monday is 1 and Sunday is 7.
[src:python/datetime-p01] Return a named tuple object with three components: `year`, `week` and `weekday`.
[src:python/datetime-p01] The ISO year consists of 52 or 53 full weeks, and where a week starts on a Monday and ends on a Sunday.
