[src:python/datetime-p02] If both comparands are aware and have different `tzinfo` attributes, the comparison acts as comparands were first converted to UTC datetimes except that the implementation never overflows.
[src:python/datetime-p02] `datetime` instances in a repeated interval are never equal to `datetime` instances in other time zone.
